<div><div><h2>--</h2></div><div>mumbai: bajaj electricals will induct pooja bajaj  wife of late managing director anant  on its board as a non-executive director in the absence of an immediate heir  a top executive close to the matter said. the 35-year-old will be gradually involved with the operations of the company.bajaj electricals is also hiring a new executive director  who will take the responsibilities of chief operating officer soon and may later be made its chief executive.after the sudden demise of anant bajaj in august  his father  70-year-old shekhar bajaj  has taken over as the managing director of the electrical goods maker.</div></div>